data.description: Discover this fabulous ranch situated in the desirable Heavenly Acres subdivision where modern luxury harmonizes with natural beauty. This inviting home features an open layout, flooded with natural light, and adorned with high-end finishes. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary haven with top-tier appliances and granite countertops. With multiple bedrooms and a lavish master suite, there's space for every family member. The expansive backyard is almost an acre that offers a tranquil retreat, perfect for morning coffee or sunset views. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this property provides easy access to schools, parks, and shopping. Don't miss the chance to call this your home! Schedule your viewing today!
